# Project Structure

Pretty straightforward layout вЂ” main.py is the entry point, everything else is split into scraper logic, database, and config folders.

I have collected 100K plus companies if you start scraper again only new will be save.
Fully resumable. To start fresh, just delete the `.db` file.

*Note:* Credentials and proxies are already configured for testing. You can run the scraper straight away without any additional setup.

## Scalable Design
Scraper can collect all companies available on AHU website without duplicate.


